This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-apps-demo layer.
This layer is meant for expermemtial purposes to exporse different technologies while building an embedded linux system:
- differences between the different init and service managers sysv and systemd
- how to build containers in yocto
- LSM like SMACK and SELinux

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded
  branch: kirkstone

Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the meta-apps-demo layer to the xxxx mailing list (xxxx@zzzz.org)
and cc: the maintainer:

Maintainer: Ahmed RAMADAN <ahmed.ramadan02@gmail.com>

